folder: Suffolk Street & Broome Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
63-65-67 Suffolk Street, at, and adjoining the N.W. corner of Broome Street. Also shown are Nos. 196-198 Broome Street, at and adjoining the N.W. corner of Suffolk Street. Nos. 63 Suffolk and 196 Broome Streets, is the same building, and has a frontage of 52.6 feet on Suffolk and only 25 feet on Broome Streets.

January 1916.

folder: Broome Street & Suffolk Street, Manhattan, NY
text:

Board of Education, N.Y.C.
April 16, 1931.

folder: Broome Street & Suffolk Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
